<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA79">
<l>paṇintum paṭarcaṭaiyāṉ pātaṅkaḷ pōtā</l>
<l>laṇintu maṇintavarai yēttat - tuṇinteṉṟu</l>
<l>mentaiyārk kāṭceyyap peṟṟa vitukolō</l>
<l>cintaiyārk kuḷḷa cerukku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To humble oneself, to adorn with buds the feet of him with spreading</l>
<l>matted hair, determined to praise those who adorn [him], to obtain</l>
<l>always to do service to our father, is this [not]</l>
<l>the pride that belongs to those who have minds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
